own-origin-found-west-coast-69301250 |title=Washington governor declares state of emergency over virus |access-date=3 March 2020 |agency=[[Associated Press]] |via=[[ABC News]]}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"oBFiI\">{{Cite news |last=Leins |first=Casey | name-list-format = vanc |url=https://www.usnews.com/news/best-states/articles/2020-03-02/washington-florida-governors-declare-state-of-emergency-for-coronavirus |title=Washington, Florida Governors Declare State of Emergency for Coronavirus |date=2 March 2020 |work=[[US News and World Report]] |access-date=2 March 2020}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"jmY4Q\">{{cite web |last1=Freiman |first1=Jordan | name-list-format = vanc |title=California governor declares State of Emergency |url=https://www.cbsnews.com/live-updates/coronavirus-outbreak-death-toll-us-infections-latest-news-updates-2020-03-04/ |publisher=[[CBS News]] |access-date=5 March 2020}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"0swfV\">{{cite news |last1=Ortiz |first1=Erik | name-list-format = vanc |title=More schools are closing because of coronavirus. Will that be the norm? |url=https://www.nbcnews.com/news/us-news/coronavirus-prompts-dozen-schools-washington-state-close-others-weigh-options-n1145496 |access-date=3 March 2020 |publisher=NBC News |date=2 March 2020}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"Wu0L3\">{{cite news |last1=Altavena |first1=Lily |last2=Londberg |first2=Max |last3=Murphy |first3=Justin | name-list-format = vanc |title=After coronavirus school closings, will states need to hold kids back, institute summer school? |url=https://www.usatoday.com/story/news/education/2020/03/18/coronavirus-school-closings-online-school-summer-school/2862873001/ |access-date=5 April 2020 |work=USA Today |location=Phoenix}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"mV0vZ\">{{cite news |title=Trump signs emergency coronavirus package, injecting $8.3&nbsp;billion into efforts to fight the outbreak |url=https://markets.businessinsider.com/news/stocks/trump-signs-billion-emergency-funding-package-fight-coronavirus-legislation-covid19-020-3-10289