jm.org/coronavirus Coronavirus (Covid-19)] by ''[[The New England Journal of Medicine]]''\n* [https://novel-coronavirus.onlinelibrary.wiley.com/ Covid-19: Novel Coronavirus] by [[Wiley (publisher)|Wiley Publishing]]\n\n{{2019\u201320 coronavirus pandemic|short=yes}}<!--Do not remove \"short=yes\" without previewing the page to make sure there is no \"Warning: Template include size is too large\" error displayed. It will not render correctly and will place this article in an error category.-->\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:2019-20 coronavirus pandemic}}\n[[Category:2019\u201320 coronavirus pandemic| ]]\n[[Category:2010s disease outbreaks]]\n[[Category:2019 disasters in Asia]]\n[[Category:2019 disasters in China]]\n[[Category:2019 health disasters]]\n[[Category:2019 in international relations]]\n[[Category:2020 disasters in Asia]]\n[[Category:2020 health disasters]]\n[[Category:2020 in international relations]]\n[[Category:2020s disease outbreaks]]\n[[Category:21st-century epidemics]]\n[[Category:Articles containing video clips]]\n[[Category:Atypical pneumonias]]\n[[Category:Current events]]\n[[Category:December 2019 events in China]]\n[[Category:February 2020 events in China]]\n[[Category:Health disasters in China]]\n[[Category:History of Wuhan]]\n[[Category:January 2020 events in China]]\n[[Category:March 2020 events in China]]\n[[Category:Occupational safety and health]]\n[[Category:Pandemics]]\n[[Category:Public Health Emergency of International Concern]]\n", "text_old": "<noinclude>{{Title notice/sandbox|1=COVID-19 pandemic|2=Talk:2019\u201320_coronavirus_pandemic#Requested_move_26_April_2020}}\n</noinclude>{{pp-protected|small=yes}}\n<!--NOTE: Please discuss on talk page before putting a \"current event\" template here. This is intended for short-term use only per advice at Template:Current. When removing content, please also remove its associated references. Thank you.-->\n{{short description|Ongoing pandemic of coronavirus disease 2019 (COVID-19)}}\n